`<sorts>` is a space separated list of sort names, `<sort>` is a 
single sort name.
`<op-spec>` can be of the following forms:

prefix-spec
  ~ the `<op-spec>` does not contain a literal `_`:
    This defines a normal prefix operator with domain `<sorts>` and
